reviewText: Realistic and informative. I'm giving it as a gift for a teen who is an aspiring veterinarian.

This DVD is very good and I highly for anyone into Animal Rights/Advocacy! Very heart breaking and sad yet gives wonderful info! A great eye opener on how animals as pets can be treated-and should be treated! I wish more cared about the animals and their pets! Please be a responsible pet owner & always adopt from a shelter!
